    <item>
      <title>How to Change the Gmail Notification Action from Archive to Delete</title>
      <link>https://dennys.github.io/en/doc/android/gmail-notify-delete-archive/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Oct 2022 06:18:32 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://dennys.github.io/en/doc/android/gmail-notify-delete-archive/</guid>
      <description>
        
          
            &lt;h2 id=&#34;requirement&#34;&gt;Requirement&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In Gmail&#39;s default notification actions, you can choose to &lt;em&gt;Archive&lt;/em&gt; or &lt;em&gt;Reply&lt;/em&gt; .
But you can change it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;
  &lt;picture&gt;

    
      
        
        
        
        
        
        
    &lt;img
      loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
      decoding=&#34;async&#34;
      alt=&#34; &#34;
      
        class=&#34;image_figure image_internal image_unprocessed&#34;
        src=&#34;https://dennys.github.io/images/software/android/email/gmail_action_archive.en.webp&#34;
      
      
    /&gt;

    &lt;/picture&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;solution&#34;&gt;Solution&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open the Gmail App&#39;s &lt;em&gt;General setting&lt;/em&gt;, change the *Default email notification action&amp;quot;.
The default action is &lt;em&gt;Archive&lt;/em&gt;, but you can change it to &lt;em&gt;Delete&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;
  &lt;picture&gt;

    
      
        
        
        
        
        
        
    &lt;img
      loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
      decoding=&#34;async&#34;
      alt=&#34; &#34;
      
        class=&#34;image_figure image_internal image_unprocessed&#34;
        src=&#34;https://dennys.github.io/images/software/android/email/gmail_notification_setup.en.webp&#34;
      
      
    /&gt;

    &lt;/picture&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;After configuring, you will be able to delete emails in Gmail&#39;s notification.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;
  &lt;picture&gt;

    
      
        
        
        
        
        
        
    &lt;img
      loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
      decoding=&#34;async&#34;
      alt=&#34; &#34;
      
        class=&#34;image_figure image_internal image_unprocessed&#34;
        src=&#34;https://dennys.github.io/images/software/android/email/gmail_action_delete.en.webp&#34;
      
      
    /&gt;

    &lt;/picture&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
          
          
        
      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Android Gmail Notification Actions (Archive, Delete, ...)</title>
      <link>https://dennys.github.io/en/doc/android/android-gmail-notification-actions/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Oct 2022 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://dennys.github.io/en/doc/android/android-gmail-notification-actions/</guid>
      <description>
        
          
            &lt;h2 id=&#34;requirement&#34;&gt;Requirement&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the previous article, we know we can change &lt;em&gt;archive&lt;/em&gt; to &lt;em&gt;delete&lt;/em&gt; in the Email(Gmail) notification of Android
(Reference: &lt;a href=&#34;http://dennys.github.io/en/doc/android/gmail-notify-delete-archive/&#34;&gt;http://dennys.github.io/en/doc/android/gmail-notify-delete-archive/&lt;/a&gt;)
But we cannot enable &lt;strong&gt;BOTH&lt;/strong&gt;, therefore, I try to find a solution in other Apps.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/thundernest/k-9&#34;&gt;K-9 Mail&lt;/a&gt;, ( &lt;a href=&#34;https://blog.thunderbird.net/2022/06/revealed-thunderbird-on-android-plans-k9/&#34;&gt;K-9 Mail Joins The Thunderbird Family&lt;/a&gt; )&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/M66B/FairEmail&#34;&gt;FairEmail&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;gmail&#34;&gt;Gmail&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Let&#39;s check Gmail&#39;s ability, the default action is &lt;em&gt;Archive&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;
  &lt;picture&gt;

    
      
        
        
        
        
        
        
    &lt;img
      loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
      decoding=&#34;async&#34;
      alt=&#34; &#34;
      
        class=&#34;image_figure image_internal image_unprocessed&#34;
        src=&#34;https://dennys.github.io/images/software/android/email/gmail_action_archive.zh-tw.webp&#34;
      
      
    /&gt;

    &lt;/picture&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open the Gmail App&#39;s &lt;em&gt;General setting&lt;/em&gt;, and change the *Default email notification action&amp;quot;.
The default action is &lt;em&gt;Archive&lt;/em&gt;, you can change it to &lt;em&gt;Delete&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;
  &lt;picture&gt;

    
      
        
        
        
        
        
        
    &lt;img
      loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
